1. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper deals with the statistical analysis of the fading end-to-end channel gain of the AF relaying protocol, which is a key concept in information theory. 
2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the performance analysis of a cooperative diversity relay network, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.COMM (Communication and Networking) - The paper deals with the analysis of the outage probability of a communication network, which is a core topic in communication and networking. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses the effect of AWGN on the network performance, which is a topic that falls under the domain of systems and control. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - Although not directly related to multimedia, the paper deals with the performance analysis of a communication network, which is a topic that can be applied to multimedia systems.
